    <criterion testable="true">`InsightsResponseRenderer.tsx` exists at `src/solutions/SpaarkeAi/src/components/conversation/insights/InsightsResponseRenderer.tsx` and is a React 19 functional component using Fluent v9 semantic tokens only (no hex / rgba / Fluent v8 imports).</criterion>
