    <criterion testable="true">Four sub-renderers exist as separate files: `PlaybookResponseRenderer`, `RagResponseRenderer`, `DeclineResponseRenderer`, `EmptyResultHint`. Each handles one render case.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Playbook path REUSES `StructuredOutputStreamWidget` (task 017) via `INSIGHTS_PLAYBOOK_SCHEMA` import â€” no parallel structured-output renderer built. Code comments cite the reuse mandate (CLAUDE.md Â§3.1) + task 017 reusability handshake.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Playbook path supports BOTH `mode: 'static'` (v1.0 single-shot â€” derives `prefilledFields` from `structuredResult.envelope`) AND `mode: 'streaming'` (v1.1 SSE â€” passes `correlationId` and lets widget subscribe to PaneEventBus deltas). Toggle controlled by `streamingEnabled` prop.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">RAG path renders `response.answer` with `[n]` citation tokens tokenized via `\[(\d+)\]` regex; each token renders as a Fluent v9 `Button appearance="transparent"` with stub `onClick` (logs via `console.debug`). Task-027 seam documented inline via `TODO(task-027)` comment.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">RAG path also renders a citation reference list (Fluent v9 `Card` with per-citation `Text` showing `[n] source â€” excerpt`) below the prose so users can read citations even before task 027 wires click dispatch.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Decline case renders `MessageBar intent="warning"` containing `response.answer` (= `DeclineResponse.Explanation`) + plain-text list of `envelope.suggestedActions`. NO Fluent buttons for actions (per integration brief Â§6 D3 v1 decision).</criterion>
