    <criterion testable="true">Decline and empty-result are visually distinct â€” decline uses `MessageBar` warning framing; empty-result uses muted `Text` with `tokens.colorNeutralForeground3`. No `MessageBar` on empty-result.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">All four render cases pass dark-mode visual check against `webDarkTheme`; evidence captured in task notes. No hex/rgba/Fluent v8 leaked into styles.</criterion>
